<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" href="/assets/book-icon.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-KyZXEAg3QhqLMpG8r+8fhAXLRk2vvoC2f3B09zVXn8CA5QIVfZOJ3BCsw2P0p/We" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>Login</title>
    <style>
    body {
      background-image: url("https://www.twosomesolutions.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/depositphotos_54615585-stock-photo-old-books-on-wooden-table-2.jpg");
      background-size: cover;
      height: 100vh;
     
     }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container justify-content-center mt-2 bg-light" style="width: 35%;border:1px solid grey;">
     <form  class="p-5" action="/register" method="POST" encType="multipart/form-data">
        <h4 class="fw-bold text-center">Registrujte se na EBiblioteku</h4>
        <p class="text-center">Registrujte se da vidite sta vasi prijatelji citaju,
          da dodajate komentare
        </p>
        <div class="form-group my-1 " >
          <label for="ime">Ime</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" required id="ime" name="ime" aria-describedby="emailHelp" placeholder="Unesi prezime">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group my-2" >
            <label for="prezime">Prezime</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="prezime" required name="prezime" aria-describedby="emailHelp" placeholder="Unesi ime">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group my-2" >
            <label for="datum">Datum rodjenja</label>
            <input type="date" class="form-control" id="datum" required name="datum" aria-describedby="emailHelp" placeholder="Unesi datum rodjenja">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group my-2" >
            <label for="nadimak">Nadimak</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="nadimak" required id="nadimak" placeholder="Nadimak">
          </div>
        <div class="form-group my-2" >
          <label for="exampleInputPassword1">Password</label>
          <input type="password" class="form-control" name="sifra" required id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="Password">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="exampleFormControlFile1">Izaberi sliku</label>
            <input type="file" class="form-control-file" name="slika" required id="exampleFormControlFile1">
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-warning mt-3 fw-bold">Submit</button>
      </form>
    </div>
      <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.3/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-eMNCOe7tC1doHpGoWe/6oMVemdAVTMs2xqW4mwXrXsW0L84Iytr2wi5v2QjrP/xp" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-cn7l7gDp0eyniUwwAZgrzD06kc/tftFf19TOAs2zVinnD/C7E91j9yyk5//jjpt/" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>